{"type": "article", "id": 28407, "title": "可以当做充电站的木柜", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-20T06:55:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021504195iR9MzNyO83mr0hu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>钉在墙上的收纳架并不少见，西班牙工作室 <a href=\"http://www.oitenta.com/\">Oitenta</a> 专门设计了一款可以用来做充电站的柜子 Floating Shelf，把插座巧妙地隐藏起来，同时又可以在内部储存一些小物。柜门还贴心地附带了一条橡皮圈，可以用它固定住充电线、钥匙、手表等常用物件。柜子的顶部可以放上书本、时钟或者是盆栽作为装饰，既实用又美观。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/281313170/minimalistic-wall-shelf-floating-shelf\">购买链接</a>，售价为 80.87 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150416tRqjZcH7ohP9Bezp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150416YnQ58Pog3Obpvf0h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021504173CJwcYtoUWkfpZDR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150418rPc1AfBMsN34S5tE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}